---
import { getCollection } from "astro:content";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const posts = await getCollection("blog");
---

<Layout title="Blog">
    <p>What is this? It seems you've stumbled upon cosmic knowledge and technological wonders!</p>
    <p>Oh, no, wait! It's just my <i>blog</i>.. Instead you may find ramblings on Linux operating systems, Bash scripting and general systems programming</p>
    <ul>{ posts.map((post) => (
        <li><a href={"/posts/" + post.slug}>{post.data.title}</a></li>
    ))}</ul>
</Layout>